{"tid":1002609,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"艾倫佩姬演繹另類超級英雄！Netflix原創美劇《雨傘學院》正式預告上線","createTime":"2019-01-31T05:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T04:00:40.000Z","uid":49391,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d089781c5eb6e19f4dfe7cd75988230b3c799047","tid":1002609,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FgG4FCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFgG4FCx.jpg&h=48037078&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNetflix 黑馬漫畫改編美劇《雨傘學院》（The Umbrella Academy）正式預告上線，由超級英雄組成的失能家庭必須在八天之內團結一心，才能拯救世界。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《雨傘學院》改編自搖滾樂隊「我的另類羅曼史」主唱傑洛德威（Gerard Way）編劇、蓋布瑞巴（Gabriel B&aacute;）繪製而成的艾斯納獎（Eisner Award）得獎系列漫畫。故事背景設定在約翰甘迺迪從未被刺殺的架空世界中，描述創立「雨傘學院」的富有企業家雷金納德哈格里夫斯爵士，又名「單眼鏡」（The Monocle）神秘身亡後，其領養的超能力子女決定搭檔合作，解開父親死亡之謎，但卻因為迥異的個性和能力而屢遭潰敗。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n正式預告以繁華都市夜景開場，旁白描述在 1989 年 10 月，世界各地有 43 位女性生下孩子，但怪異的是她們在生產前根本沒有懷孕。隨後其中一群孩子被「單眼鏡」領養，在「雨傘學院」成長，各自在展現一些超乎常人的能力後，畫面直接跳到 17 年之後。被領養的孩子們皆已成年，他們在養父死後團聚，2 號成員「海怪」說出一句「他是怪物」後，揭開這個家長久以來的瘋狂。在得知世界即將毀滅，他們除了必須齊心協力，還得應付意圖讓他們喪命的殺手們。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n▼《雨傘學院》第一季正式預告。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nAzqnUDARW4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnAzqnUDARW4&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6r%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=5f622f03\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nAzqnUDARW4</a><br />\n<br />\n卡司陣容包括《冰與火之歌：權力遊戲》湯姆霍珀（Tom Hopper）飾演「太空男孩」（Spaceboy）、《怒火邊界2：毒刑者》大衛卡斯塔尼達（David Casta&ntilde;eda）飾演「海怪」（The Kraken）、《怪媽闖蕩記》艾美瑞佛蘭普曼（Emmy Raver-Lampman）飾演「謠言家」（The Rumor）、《天使聖物:骸骨之城》羅伯席安（Robert Sheehan）飾演「降神」（The S&eacute;ance）、《尼奇、瑞奇、迪奇和曙光》艾丹蓋勒（Aidan Gallagher）飾演「五號」（Number Five）以及《全面啟動》艾倫佩姬（Ellen Page）飾演「白色小提琴」（The White Violin）。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《雨傘學院》第一季共十集將於 2 月 15 日在全球 Netflix 上線。（YouTube、Netflix Center Media）"},{"pid":"754f2713ddb0c778cf798e891d2aee053dea9963","tid":1002609,"uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:30:28.000Z","msg":"幻影貓轉職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45cd4c25863e852623eb4e83ec238db62b190a50","tid":1002609,"uid":48295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:33:24.000Z","msg":"Gerard Way好勁"},{"pid":"6dfc8f192bbb265b4366a5b64b164e9a28b28dd1","tid":1002609,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"754f2713ddb0c778cf798e891d2aee053dea9963","tid":1002609,"uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:30:28.000Z","msg":"幻影貓轉職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T07:15:39.000Z","msg":"Ellen book好正"},{"pid":"b8f3335ffed5ff52fe65b28fbb0174b1fd4000bb","tid":1002609,"uid":208809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:15:30.000Z","msg":"Gerard Way<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c594bb7eeb8e19b7930160ce348638882d61596","tid":1002609,"uid":56223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:18:12.000Z","msg":"when you go<br />\nwould you have the guts to say<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2775680baf972bc2cdc41580c74ef54e97215a42","tid":1002609,"uid":41963,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:15:05.000Z","msg":"又見到全面啟動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebb043d4a6c70c289f956f5845758b078ca7751","tid":1002609,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2775680baf972bc2cdc41580c74ef54e97215a42","tid":1002609,"uid":41963,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:15:05.000Z","msg":"又見到全面啟動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:23:47.000Z","msg":"原本都估唔到係邊套戲<br />\n睇多幾次就記得左"},{"pid":"a4063edb9c2a